        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "Pls see below for routes.xml and navigation.xml.\r\n\r\nWhen I go to:\r\n\r\n{noformat}\r\nhttp:\/\/www.example.com\/en_US\/default\/index\/index\/\r\n{noformat} \r\n\r\nI would expect:\r\n\r\n{noformat}\r\n<?php echo $this->activeNavigation()->get('title'); ?>\r\n<?php echo $this->activeNavigation()->get('label'); ?>\r\n{noformat} \r\n\r\nin the View to output:\r\n\r\n{noformat}\r\nHome\r\nHome\r\n{noformat} \r\n\r\nas it does in ZF 1.11.7 and earlier.\r\n\r\nIn ZF 1.11.8, \r\n\r\n{noformat}\r\n<?php Zend_Debug::dump($this->activeNavigation()); ?>\r\n{noformat} \r\n\r\nreturns \r\n\r\n{noformat}\r\nNULL\r\n{noformat} \r\n\r\nand it should return:\r\n\r\n{noformat}\r\nobject(Zend_Navigation_Page_Mvc)#54 (24) { [...] }\r\n{noformat}\r\n\r\nBy overwriting the method Zend_Navigation_Page_Mvc::isActive in ZF 1.11.8 with the method Zend_Navigation_Page_Mvc::isActive from ZF 1.11.7 the issue can be resolved.\r\n\r\nThe issue, it would seem, is caused by the last fix in Zend_Navigation_Page_Mvc::isActive in ZF 1.11.8.\r\n\r\nThis is a \"Blocker\", as it break the entire web site.\r\n\r\n\r\nroutes.xml:\r\n\r\n{noformat}\r\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n\r\n<config>\r\n\r\n    <routes>\r\n\r\n        <default>\r\n            <route>:locale\/:module\/:controller\/:action\/*<\/route>\r\n            <defaults>\r\n                <locale \/>\r\n                <module>default<\/module>\r\n                <controller>index<\/controller>\r\n                <action>index<\/action>\r\n            <\/defaults>\r\n            <reqs>\r\n                <locale>.*<\/locale>\r\n                <module>.*<\/module>\r\n                <controller>.*<\/controller>\r\n                <action>.*<\/action>\r\n            <\/reqs>\r\n        <\/default>\r\n\r\n    <\/routes>\r\n\r\n<\/config>\r\n{noformat}\r\n\r\n\r\nnavigation.xml:\r\n\r\n{noformat}\r\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n\r\n<config>\r\n    <root>\r\n        <type>Zend_Navigation_Page_Mvc<\/type>\r\n        <route>default<\/route>\r\n        <module>default<\/module>\r\n        <controller>index<\/controller>\r\n        <action>index<\/action>\r\n        <label>Home<\/label>\r\n        <title>Home<\/title>\r\n    <\/root>\r\n<\/config>\r\n{noformat}"
        },
